Rating: 4
Warning: this pie is addictive! I usually modify recipes to suit my own whims, but I followed this one to the letter and don't think much could be done to improve upon it! The struesel topping bakes into a heavenly sweet crisp; I served this at Thanksgiving while it was still warm, with a good quality vanilla ice cream, and it sent everyone into a swoon! Be sure to stick with a good, tart baking apple for this recipe; the sweetness of the crisp counteracts the tartness of the apples beautifully.

